* Apply Iterative\nRefinement
** Ongoing process, not one-time setup
** Test yourself first
***_ Ask expected business user questions
***_ Review generated SQL carefully
** Fix incorrect responses
***_ Show generated code
***_ Edit SQL and save as instruction
** Benchmark questions
***_ Common questions with expected answers
***_ Run regularly to measure improvement
** User feedback
***_ Rating mechanism in Genie
***_ Review Monitoring tab
***_ Adjust instructions based on patterns
@endmindmap
